{"tid":245562,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)狂蟒之災1-2 關鍵第四號 天龍特攻隊","createTime":"2017-05-16T10:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T17:32:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34e99afebca23f75cac5e2b8ccd5bca7ab59e17f","tid":245562,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7eae45bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=098be9d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=64b0f24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7c/Anaconda_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7c%2FAnaconda_poster.jpg&h=ae3890a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/62/I_Am_Number_Four_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F6%2F62%2FI_Am_Number_Four_Poster.jpg&h=a80441a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bc/The_A-Team.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbc%2FThe_A-Team.jpg&h=4aadffa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在地球上的南美洲亞馬遜河流域，居住著一個民族舒爾族，他們一直和外界都沒有聯繫和溝通，顯得神秘而令人神往，他們崇拜的圖騰是巨蟒蛇。<br />\n美國的科學家們對舒爾族有著濃厚的興趣，他們組團前往去探究。人類學家史蒂文&middot;凱和紀錄片導演泰莉&middot;勞瑞帶著7他的團隊跟從一個名叫保羅&middot;沙龍的嚮導邁入了亞馬遜熱帶雨林，他們的隊伍中混雜著偷獵者，妄圖將巨蟒蛇抓住，賣到美國去大賺一筆，由於貪心和狂妄，他們從此一去不復返，全部被巨蟒蛇殺害.........<br />\n<br />\n2.一群科學家打著尋找神秘植物「血蘭」的名號進入尚未開發的婆羅洲地區，科學家相信血蘭具有一種神奇的功效，可以使人永葆青春，永不衰老。美國紐約州紐約市的一家公司對血蘭的藥理功效非常感興趣，他們希望找到這種植物，然後大賺一筆，於是慷慨解囊，資助了這些缺乏資金的科學家。科學家選擇了一個不恰當的時機出發，就是蟒蛇交配和雨季，而血蘭這種神奇的植物生長在蟒蛇的地盤上，為了掠奪血蘭，他們開始和蟒蛇一較高下，決一生死.....<br />\n<br />\n3.一名來自羅瑞恩行星的外星人（艾力克斯&middot;派帝佛 飾）為了逃離一群來自摩加多利恩行星，摧毀他們故鄉的侵略者，在孩提時代與另外八名同伴被送往了地球。在他身邊有一名守護者（提摩西&middot;奧力芬 飾）負責保護他的生命安全，而他本身的能力也漸漸的覺醒，像是力氣的增強、速度、靈敏度、心靈傳動能力、能對抗高熱與火焰，以及從手掌中發光..<br />\n<br />\n4. 同樣身為美國陸軍遊騎兵，約翰&middot;&quot;漢尼拔&quot;&middot;史密斯、派克&middot;斐斯、拜庫斯&middot;博斯克和默多克四人曾經在墨西哥和黑暗勢力鬥爭時結成好友，組成了「天龍特攻隊」。一日，美國將軍莫里森找到他們，請他們幫助美國軍方找回丟失在伊拉克戰爭中的美元鈔票模板，四人在伊拉克巴格達找到了假冒的美元鈔票模板，卻被幕後人物布拉德&middot;帕克奪走，而天龍特攻隊也因被誣陷而關進了監獄..<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0739f905b0a8b1d299ebe14f02df04ba8925d8c","tid":245562,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024b5e508adc0a9a28303bf9a148e7869a750cf9","tid":245562,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2701a373078aeca2803b485cfc8a8220f43c88f2","tid":245562,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16